Complete Google Apps Script Project Delivery Protocol

Compliance Acknowledgment

"I confirm this delivery includes the complete, unabridged, executable Google Apps Script project with all functions, classes, configuration, imports, error handling, HTML/UI components, and implementation instructions, with no omissions or placeholders."

Core Requirement

Provide the full, executable Google Apps Script project‚Äîno omissions, no summaries, no placeholders. Deliver every line necessary to run, test, and integrate the solution exactly as specified below.

Definition of "Complete" for Google Apps Script Projects

Your delivery must include all of the following, in full:

Code Components

All code: Every function, method, class, and utility from declaration/opening to closing bracket

Control flow: Full if/else, switch/match, loops, early returns, and guards

Error handling: Complete exception handling paths, validations, and recovery logic

Dependencies: All Apps Script services (SpreadsheetApp, UrlFetchApp, etc.) and any library references

Configuration: Concrete configuration values, script properties, and clearly labeled environment variable references

Data access: Complete Sheets queries, API calls, data transformation logic, and UI interactions

State & variables: All declarations, initializations, assignments, and mutations

Comments & docs: Meaningful inline comments and JSDoc sufficient for review and maintenance

Event handlers: All trigger functions (onOpen, onEdit, doGet, doPost) fully implemented

UI Components

Complete HTML: Full markup structure from <!DOCTYPE html> to </html>

Inline CSS: All styling rules, responsive design, and visual enhancements

Client-side scripts: All JavaScript for UI interactions, server calls, and event handling

Apps Script integration: Complete google.script.run calls with success/failure handlers

Configuration

Manifest file: Complete appscript.json with all required services, scopes, and settings

Dependencies: Any required libraries with proper version specifications

Prohibited: Ellipses (...), "omitted for brevity," "// rest of code here," partial stubs, redactions, or condensed pseudocode.

Deliverable Structure

Present the complete project with each file as a separate, clearly labeled markdown code block with syntax highlighting. Provide them in this order:

1. code.gs (Apps Script Backend Code)

Format: Markdown code block with javascript syntax highlighting

Must Include:

All function declarations with complete implementations

All helper/utility functions fully written out

Complete error handling and validation logic

All Apps Script service integrations (SpreadsheetApp, etc.)

Event handlers (onOpen, onEdit, doGet, doPost) with full logic

Data access patterns with complete queries and transformations

Complete function signatures with parameter documentation

JSDoc comments for public functions

All variable declarations and state management

Complete control flow without omissions

Structure Requirements:

/**

* Complete JSDoc description

* @param {Type} paramName - Description

* @return {Type} Description

*/

