// Full implementation here

// All error handling

// All business logic

// All return paths

}

Ensure:

Code is fully functional and production-ready

All edge cases are handled

No placeholder functions or TODO comments

Includes meaningful inline comments for clarity

2. HTML File (Frontend/UI Code)

Format: Markdown code block with html syntax highlighting

Must Include:

Complete HTML document structure (DOCTYPE, html, head, body tags)

All UI elements and form controls

Inline CSS with complete styling rules

Client-side JavaScript with full implementation

All event listeners and handlers

Complete google.script.run integration with success/failure callbacks

Loading states and error handling UI

Input validation logic

Complete user interaction flows

Structure Requirements:

