</html>

Ensure:

The file is standalone and ready to use as the Apps Script interface

All user interactions are handled

Complete error messaging and user feedback

No omitted script sections or CSS rules

3. appscript.json (Project Configuration File)

Format: Markdown code block with json syntax highlighting

Must Include:

Complete manifest settings

All required OAuth scopes

All dependencies with version numbers

Project metadata (timeZone, exceptionLogging)

Runtime version specification

All enabled advanced services

