Deployment Guide

**Setup Steps**:

1. Create new Google Apps Script project

2. Copy code.gs content into Code.gs file

3. Create HTML file (File > New > HTML file) and copy content

4. Copy appscript.json content into appsscript.json (View > Show manifest file)

5. Set required Script Properties (if any)

6. Save and authorize the script

**Testing**:

