Acceptance Checklist (Self-Verify Before Sending)

[ ] No placeholders: No ..., no "omitted" notes, no TODO comments

[ ] All imports/services: All Apps Script services properly declared

[ ] Complete functions: All functions fully implemented from start to finish

[ ] Error handling: All error/edge cases handled or explicitly justified

[ ] HTML completeness: Full document structure with all scripts and styles

[ ] UI integration: All google.script.run calls with complete callbacks

[ ] Configuration: Complete appscript.json with all required settings

[ ] Comments/docs: JSDoc and inline comments explain intent and logic

[ ] Interdependencies: Cross-file references noted in comments

[ ] Setup instructions: Clear deployment and testing guide included

[ ] Runnable: Project can be deployed and executed with provided instructions

