Installable Triggers

Installable triggers are more powerful and flexible but require setup and authorization.

Characteristics:

Must be programmatically created

Full access to Google services

Longer execution time limits (6 minutes)

Can send emails, access Drive, etc.

More reliable and robust

Can be managed and monitored

